# Verification Quality Checklist — <story id>
<!-- Generated to docs/checklists/verification-<id>.md. Check before shipping a story. -->

- [ ] Deterministic gates (test/lint/build) were run and recorded — green or explicit N/A.
- [ ] Reviewer verdicts are recorded for every selected lens.
- [ ] All `block` / `major` findings are resolved.
- [ ] Every acceptance criterion is checked against actual behaviour.
- [ ] `git status` / `git diff` were inspected — only the story's files changed.
- [ ] `pm-verifier` returned STATUS: PASS before shipping.
